# Stack Constraints

## Allowed stack
- Frontend: Next.js (App Router), React Hook Form, TanStack Query, shadcn/ui, Tailwind
- Backend: NestJS (TypeScript strict)
- DB: PostgreSQL with Prisma

## Forbidden
- Redux
- SWR
- TypeORM / Sequelize
- MongoDB
- Express standalone (outside NestJS)

## Rules
- All server state must use TanStack Query
- All forms must use React Hook Form
- All DB access must go through Prisma